-TRANSACTION TABLE:- 



Get the total transactions performed in Chennai.

( To get the dump of this data export the table  SQL file into CSV)


Get all the records of ”Mark001” that have “USD”currency 

There are only 2  sales in Chennai with USD currency.





Perform INNER JOIN  to Show Transactions in 2020 JOIN BY date table.

CODE FOR INNER JOIN:-
SELECT sales.transactions.*, sales.date.* FROM sales.transactions INNER JOIN sales.date ON sales.transactions.order_date=sales.date.date                    


Get the total revenue in year 2020.

Revenue in year 2019.
 
NOTE:- sales have declined in year 2020.

CODE:-
SELECT SUM(sales.transactions.sales_amount) FROM sales.transactions 
INNER JOIN sales.date ON sales.transactions.order_date=sales.date.date
WHERE  sales.date.year=2020; 


